	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />"Game Paks" and "Cartridges" are both printed circuit boards which contain address and data pins to allow the rom chips to be directly addressable by the CPU.
<br />
<br />"Game Cards" are not directly addressable.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


